"{\"uid\": \"today.com-health-men-s-health-brody-malone-gymnastics-olympics-injury-rcna164156\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Michael Kors Bag, Suede Slippers and More Holiday Gifts at Walmart - Starting at $9    Liz Calvario  Editor/Reporter  It was a day for celebration when the United States men's gymnastics team made history,earning their first team medalat the Olympics since 2008.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 158, \"end\": 171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8607346616600272, \"rank\": 0.15780015493280186, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brody Malone, along with Frederick Richard, Paul Juda, Asher Hong andStephen Nedoroscik, took home the bronze medal during the men's gymnastics team finals on July 29.\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 266, \"end\": 271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicholas_Brody\", \"score\": 0.9997499833521428, \"rank\": 0.0002464641880657855, \"text\": \"Brody\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicholas_Brody\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicholas_Brody\"}, {\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"score\": 0.9979421838998328, \"rank\": 0.0015714164110111708, \"text\": \"Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}, {\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.49570655892924e-17, \"text\": \"Frederick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\"}, {\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Juda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paul Juda\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Juda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Juda\"}, {\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asher_Hong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Asher Hong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asher_Hong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asher_Hong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japan took the gold, while China won the silver.\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9537774503554343, \"rank\": 0.024599870080167605, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 461, \"end\": 466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.48412244514487224, \"rank\": 0.6479282986595831, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While onTODAY July 30, Malone reflected on the team's strong delivery following what he describes as not his \\\"best performance\\\" in the men's gymnastics qualification round on July 27.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"score\": 0.9979421838998328, \"rank\": 0.0015714164110111708, \"text\": \"Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We came here to win a team medal, so I just went back to the gym, kind of reset my mind, reset my basics,\\\" Malone said.\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"score\": 0.9979421838998328, \"rank\": 0.0015714164110111708, \"text\": \"Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went into that competition confident that I was going to be able to hit for the team.\\\"\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Malone also gave insight into their group huddle done after every event, which serves as a team reminder to stay in their \\\"bubble\\\" in order to focus on their own performance versus the competition.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA's bronze is only their third team medal in 20 years, making it an emotional moment for the athletes, including Malone whose gymnastics career was almost over after a knee injury in 2023.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9922532160997976, \"rank\": 0.005104545469422726, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"score\": 0.9979421838998328, \"rank\": 0.0015714164110111708, \"text\": \"Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You never really know how bad you want something until you get it taken away from you,\\\" Malone, 24, toldNBC2 Newsin Fort Myers, Florida, ahead of their big win.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Myers,_Florida\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fort Myers, Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Myers,_Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Myers,_Florida\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After competing in the Tokyo Olympics and not medaling, Malone set his sights on Paris.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1496, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"score\": 0.9979421838998328, \"rank\": 0.0015714164110111708, \"text\": \"Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}, {\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999972915248, \"rank\": 2.708260725058068e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, he hit a bump in the road as he continued training and competing.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the DTB Cup in Germany in March 2023, Malone slipped off the high bar as he was going for his dismount.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7873001968476825, \"rank\": 0.1856526267530591, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"score\": 0.9979421838998328, \"rank\": 0.0015714164110111708, \"text\": \"Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He would go on to tear multiple ligaments in his knee and fracture his tibia.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His full diagnosis, according toTeam USA: a torn meniscus, tibial plateau fracture, partially torn posterior cruciate ligament and fully torn lateral collateral ligament.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Malone underwent three surgeries, followed by weeks of bedrest and rehabbing for a year.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Malone would go on to prove that he had made a comeback when he won his third U.S. title in Forth Worth, Texas, in June of this year.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2144, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Worth,_Texas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Forth Worth, Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Worth,_Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Worth,_Texas\"}, {\"begin\": 2144, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Worth,_Texas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Forth Worth, Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Worth,_Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Worth,_Texas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tennessee native and Georgia-raised athlete recalled to NBC the moment he injured himself.\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2247, \"end\": 2250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9860084768693884, \"rank\": 0.014189962307047286, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt my knee go out, just like a lot of pressure, and kind of like a bang,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was catastrophic ...\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like, 'I do not know if I am going to be able to make a comeback.\\\"\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2468, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Malone added that it's \\\"an honor\\\" and \\\"a blessing\\\" to be able to compete in the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2565, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In an additional interview with Team USA, he explained that preparing for Paris he had to wear a brace when he competes and limit his time on the floor exercises and vault.\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2599, \"end\": 2607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9922532160997976, \"rank\": 0.005104545469422726, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2641, \"end\": 2646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999972915248, \"rank\": 2.708260725058068e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My approach on floor and vault is looking a little bit different.\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not trying to get as much difficulty on those events.\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am trying to just do a little bit easier routine and just hit and be clean,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It just feels amazing with everything I have gone through to make a comeback like I have.\\\"\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock is streaming the Paris Olympics around the clock.Learn more about accounts here.\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TODAY\\u00a0earns a commission on purchases.\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock is owned by our parent company NBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3215, \"end\": 3227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999998199164273, \"rank\": 1.7814817306507615e-07, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Liz Calvario is a Los Angeles-based reporter and editor for TODAY.com who covers entertainment, pop culture and trending news.\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3290, \"end\": 3299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_(American_TV_program)\", \"score\": 0.9998395956472322, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TODAY.com\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_(American_TV_program)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_(American_TV_program)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9\\u00a02025 NBCUniversal Media, LLCApple\\u00ae, Apple logo\\u00ae and App Store\\u00ae are registered trademarks of Apple Inc.\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3462, \"e